♪Memories of the past are always vivid♪

2
00:00:25,540 --> 00:00:28,340
♪They accompanied me to take every step♪

3
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:32,380
♪On the road♪

4
00:00:35,260 --> 00:00:39,060
♪Going through heat and cold♪

5
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:42,900
♪The bumpy journey
has rendered my longing♪

6
00:00:43,780 --> 00:00:46,820
♪Rock solid♪

7
00:00:47,740 --> 00:00:53,420
♪The same moonlight
shines on our shoulders♪

8
00:00:53,980 --> 00:00:57,060
♪Even if we are far away separated♪

9
00:00:57,660 --> 00:01:02,700
♪We are close in our hearts♪

10
00:01:05,860 --> 00:01:07,340
♪The wind blew away the past♪

11
00:01:07,620 --> 00:01:12,860
♪I look for your distant location
on the starry night♪

12
00:01:13,020 --> 00:01:14,460
♪In the ocean of faces♪

13
00:01:14,740 --> 00:01:20,100
♪For you, my heart burns and races♪

14
