♪May waiting convert regrets
into a happy ending♪

16
00:01:28,260 --> 00:01:34,220
♪May solitary figures
find right companions♪

17
00:01:34,980 --> 00:01:37,100
♪And become a pair♪

18
00:01:39,100 --> 00:01:43,180
=Time Flies and You Are Here=

19
00:01:43,420 --> 00:01:44,980
=Episode 5=

20
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,716
(Too bad the long song is
wasted in the evening)

21
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,040
What is it?

22
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:08,519
Are you going to reprimand me
on behalf of His Majesty?

23
00:02:09,040 --> 00:02:10,519
I'm Xie Xiaoman's senior.

24
00:02:10,959 --> 00:02:12,160
I'm also an old friend of her.

25
00:02:12,720 --> 00:02:13,599
Since she's an old friend,

26
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,119
I must protect her.

27
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:17,119
A woman's reputation is everything.

28
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:18,800
Your Highness,

29
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:20,399
on whose authority that you detain her?

30
00:02:22,559 --> 00:02:23,559
Whose authority?

31
00:02:23,620 --> 00:02:27,020
(Commandery Prince's Mansion)

32
00:02:31,479 --> 00:02:32,600
(Commandery Prince's Mansion Contract)
A system is governed by law.

33
00:02:33,080 --> 00:02:34,240
Humans are governed
by personal contracts.

34
00:02:35,000 --> 00:02:37,360
The daughter of Xie household,
Xiaoman signed a personal agreement

35
00:02:37,360 --> 00:02:38,559
with the Commandery Prince's Mansion

36
00:02:38,559 --> 00:02:39,800
as a female attendant.

37
00:02:39,919 --> 00:02:41,119
The contract lasts for two years long.

38
00:02:42,160 --> 00:02:42,919
What?

39
00:02:52,759 --> 00:02:54,440
Xie Xiaoman signed
an agreement with me.

40
00:02:55,440 --> 00:02:56,679
She's now an attendant of mine.

41
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,600
What's the matter?

42
00:02:59,800 --> 00:03:00,960
Do you want to meddle in

43
00:03:00,960 --> 00:03:01,839
with the matters of my household?

44
00:03:06,279 --> 00:03:06,919
Congwen.

45
00:03:08,720 --> 00:03:10,199
She created this mess herself.

46
00:03:10,800 --> 00:03:12,360
Even if we reported this matter
to Sir Yan,

47
00:03:12,759 --> 00:03:14,000
it wouldn't make sense.

48
00:03:24,399 --> 00:03:25,000
Congwen,

49
00:03:25,320 --> 00:03:26,479
His Highness is enraged.

50
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:27,919
You should return.

51
00:03:28,440 --> 00:03:30,279
I'll send her back tomorrow.

52
00:03:43,320 --> 00:03:44,600
I'm staying here today.

53
00:03:45,240 --> 00:03:46,039
Early in the morning tomorrow,

54
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,479
I'll send Xiaoman back home.

55
00:03:50,440 --> 00:03:51,279
Sorry

56
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,919
for the trouble, Sir Chang.

57
00:03:53,759 --> 00:03:56,479
I shall beg for you pardon
personally next time.

58
00:04:04,600 --> 00:04:05,119
Well,

59
00:04:05,839 --> 00:04:08,039
I'll leave Xiaoman to your care.

60
00:04:15,279 --> 00:04:16,080
Your Highness,

61
00:04:16,839 --> 00:04:19,360
we should prioritise peace and harmony!

62
00:04:41,720 --> 00:04:42,559
About the incident today,

63
00:04:43,600 --> 00:04:44,519
are you aware of your mistake?

64
00:04:45,920 --> 00:04:46,920
You should know

65
00:04:48,519 --> 00:04:50,040
how important today is

66
00:04:50,959 --> 00:04:51,839
to my uncle.

67
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,079
You're the Commandery Prince.

68
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:58,320
You have the authority over everyone.

69
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,440
You may exercise power
over everyone else.

70
00:05:00,600 --> 00:05:02,399
I'm just a regular commoner.

71
00:05:02,839 --> 00:05:03,839
There's nothing I can say.

72
00:05:04,720 --> 00:05:06,320
You disdained my reputation.

73
00:05:08,000 --> 00:05:08,600
Fine.

74
00:05:09,839 --> 00:05:10,640
Very well.

75
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,519
I'm telling you.

76
00:05:15,839 --> 00:05:17,000
I loathe you.

77
00:05:18,519 --> 00:05:20,720
You have no respect for others.
I hate you.

78
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:23,119
You're adamant and cocky. I hate you.

79
00:05:23,959 --> 00:05:24,720
I hate you the most

80
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,839
for trampling on the pride of others.

81
00:05:35,200 --> 00:05:36,239
You're the Commandery Prince.

82
00:05:37,440 --> 00:05:38,480
You're superior.

83
00:05:39,600 --> 00:05:41,160
I'm as insignificant as dust.

84
00:05:43,239 --> 00:05:44,880
I plead of you to leave me alone.

85
00:05:46,279 --> 00:05:47,320
Live your life as
the Commandery Prince.

86
00:05:48,359 --> 00:05:49,959
I shall live mine as a humble commoner.

87
00:05:50,880 --> 00:05:51,920
From now on, I shall do my best

88
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,440
to attend to the matters
of the household.

89
00:05:53,959 --> 00:05:54,720
However,

90
00:05:56,799 --> 00:05:58,279
you and I no longer have
anything to do with each other.

91
00:05:58,279 --> 00:05:58,760
You...

92
00:06:03,799 --> 00:06:04,359
Fine.

93
00:06:05,920 --> 00:06:06,920
Since you are so stubborn,

94
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:09,679
kneel before the Zhuiyuan Hall

95
00:06:10,839 --> 00:06:12,079
until you're willing to repent!

96
00:06:12,959 --> 00:06:14,559
It's humid at night. This is...

97
00:06:15,079 --> 00:06:15,679
Hanchen.

98
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:18,760
Xiaoman.

99
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,399
Xiaoman.

100
00:06:22,279 --> 00:06:22,839
Xiaoman.

101
00:06:27,839 --> 00:06:29,040
Back then,
the Emperor did not bear a son.

102
00:06:30,399 --> 00:06:31,679
When Hanchen was five,

103
00:06:32,119 --> 00:06:33,799
He was brought to the palace
with his old brother.

104
00:06:36,399 --> 00:06:37,279
They were both adopted,

105
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,279
but they didn't have a good time here.

106
00:06:43,279 --> 00:06:44,679
However, we both know

107
00:06:45,760 --> 00:06:47,600
what life in the palace is like.

108
00:06:49,519 --> 00:06:50,480
When he was seven,

109
00:06:51,040 --> 00:06:52,839
his brother passed away
at the East Palace.

110
00:06:53,720 --> 00:06:54,959
When Xiaojie passed away,

111
00:06:54,959 --> 00:06:56,079
Hanchen stayed by his body

112
00:06:56,079 --> 00:06:57,959
for a day and night before
the attendants discovered them.

113
00:06:59,679 --> 00:07:00,359
Afterward,

114
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,959
His Majesty was given a son,
the current crown prince.

115
00:07:04,160 --> 00:07:05,279
For the Emperor,

116
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,399
Hanchen became insignificant then.

117
00:07:07,399 --> 00:07:08,920
Four years after Xiaojie's death,

118
00:07:09,239 --> 00:07:10,519
Hanchen was sent out of the palace.

119
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,200
When he left the palace,

120
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:15,040
he was already 11 years old.

121
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,279
Prince Pu had many heirs,

122
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:20,079
but the children do not get along.

123
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,359
Hanchen entered the palace
when he was young.

124
00:07:22,640 --> 00:07:23,839
He was abandoned and
neglected by his parents.

125
00:07:24,359 --> 00:07:25,359
Why did you think

126
00:07:26,279 --> 00:07:28,160
he'd come all the way to
Wujiang Prefecture to recuperate?

127
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,200
He didn't come to recuperate,

128
00:07:31,119 --> 00:07:32,040
he came to avoid all

129
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,480
the political strife.

130
00:07:34,399 --> 00:07:35,200
Can you imagine

131
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:37,600
how difficult his life was back then?

132
00:07:38,839 --> 00:07:39,760
A young boy

133
00:07:40,160 --> 00:07:42,000
surviving in the palace all alone.

134
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:43,160
Once he left the palace,

135
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,279
he thought he'd finally feel
his family's warmth.

136
00:07:44,480 --> 00:07:46,160
Instead, he was lonelier.

137
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,279
That's why

138
00:07:49,239 --> 00:07:50,559
he may behave unreasonably.

139
00:07:51,760 --> 00:07:52,519
I hope for

140
00:07:55,440 --> 00:07:56,279
your understanding.

141
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,880
He has his hardships.

142
00:08:07,000 --> 00:08:07,799
I understand that.

143
00:08:09,519 --> 00:08:11,200
However, it doesn't justify him

144
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,640
to inflict pain upon others.

145
00:08:14,880 --> 00:08:16,440
I have my load of hardships, too.

146
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:18,640
Excuse me.

147
00:08:42,540 --> 00:08:44,740
(Zhuiyuan Hall)

148
00:09:30,280 --> 00:09:31,359
You silly girl.

149
00:10:30,060 --> 00:10:34,780
(Commandery Prince's Mansion)

150
00:10:36,440 --> 00:10:36,919
Xiaoman.

151
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:45,559
Xiaoman.

152
00:10:46,159 --> 00:10:46,919
Are you all right?

153
00:10:51,760 --> 00:10:52,960
You can take a day off from school.

154
00:10:54,479 --> 00:10:55,919
You were up all night.

155
00:10:56,359 --> 00:10:58,080
I took a leave from the principal
on your behalf.

156
00:10:59,119 --> 00:11:00,039
Allow me to send you home.

157
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:01,520
Your family must be concerned.

158
00:11:32,239 --> 00:11:34,760
Over the years since the establishment
of Bailu Academy,

159
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:37,039
the academy sought to cultivate

160
00:11:37,400 --> 00:11:40,039
men as true scholars.

161
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:41,679
You should know,

162
00:11:42,239 --> 00:11:45,119
those who seek to advocate
morality of the world,

163
00:11:45,679 --> 00:11:47,080
should first govern one's country.

164
00:11:47,679 --> 00:11:49,080
Those who seek to govern one's country,

165
00:11:49,400 --> 00:11:50,919
should first manage one's household.

166
00:11:51,200 --> 00:11:52,640
Those who seek to manage
one's household,

167
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:54,520
should first rectify one's character.

168
00:11:55,159 --> 00:11:57,320
Rectify the thoughts,
and purify one's heart.

169
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,799
Expand one's knowledge

170
00:11:59,119 --> 00:12:01,760
(Dongguan Building)
before peace could befall the state.

171
00:12:02,799 --> 00:12:04,559
A gentleman's heart knows no limits.

172
00:12:04,799 --> 00:12:07,400
His patience is boundless and vast.

173
00:12:09,280 --> 00:12:11,000
This is the question of the day.

174
00:12:11,640 --> 00:12:13,479
What defines a gentleman?

175
00:12:26,260 --> 00:12:28,380
(Capital)

176
00:12:29,406 --> 00:12:31,919
Hanchen is not coming back again?

177
00:12:32,520 --> 00:12:33,119
Yes.

178
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:35,440
It's a letter from Principal Yang.

179
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:38,080
Apparently, the prince attempts to study

180
00:12:38,080 --> 00:12:39,640
Spring and Autumn Annals from
him at Wujiang Prefecture

181
00:12:39,640 --> 00:12:40,440
before returning.

182
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:41,960
Spring and Autumn Annals?

183
00:12:42,360 --> 00:12:43,760
(Zhao Xiaoqian's mother,
Princess Consort Pu)

184
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,280
He's rather diligent.

185
00:12:46,119 --> 00:12:47,039
It's a pity.

186
00:12:47,719 --> 00:12:49,760
His diligence is in vain.

187
00:12:50,479 --> 00:12:51,280
He can't possibly

188
00:12:51,799 --> 00:12:52,960
plan to become an imperial official.

189
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:55,800
(Princess Consort Pu's nanny,
Zhu Momo)

190
00:12:56,479 --> 00:12:57,719
Deliver a letter to Wujiang Prefecture

191
00:12:58,400 --> 00:12:59,559
with the prince's seal.

192
00:13:00,359 --> 00:13:01,280
Inform Hanchen

193
00:13:02,000 --> 00:13:03,359
that he's no longer young.

194
00:13:04,239 --> 00:13:06,119
Shen family cannot afford
to wait for him anymore.

195
00:13:06,799 --> 00:13:08,000
It's time for him to get married.

196
00:13:08,880 --> 00:13:09,400
Yes.

197
00:13:09,799 --> 00:13:10,960
I shall attend to it immediately.

198
00:13:19,220 --> 00:13:20,860
(Zhiwei Hall)

199
00:13:21,159 --> 00:13:22,640
I heard that your sister

200
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,239
was in great trouble a few days ago.

201
00:13:25,559 --> 00:13:27,159
She has brought shame to the family.

202
00:13:27,440 --> 00:13:28,080
She's truly

203
00:13:28,080 --> 00:13:29,599
unruly and adamant.

204
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,799
She believes if she becomes an attendant
at the Commandery Prince's Mansion,

205
00:13:31,799 --> 00:13:33,239
she'd be able to win over
the Commandery Prince himself.

206
00:13:34,520 --> 00:13:36,000
Gossiping behind one's back.

207
00:13:36,479 --> 00:13:37,359
Both of you

208
00:13:37,599 --> 00:13:39,039
are truly despicable.

209
00:13:39,479 --> 00:13:40,359
Despicable?

210
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,000
A woman

211
00:13:42,280 --> 00:13:44,039
drawing attention to
herself out in public

212
00:13:44,039 --> 00:13:45,679
already shows profligacy.

213
00:13:46,000 --> 00:13:47,880
She resorted to
becoming an attendant

214
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,679
of the prince.

215
00:13:49,200 --> 00:13:50,880
The female students of our academy

216
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:52,119
are of prestige and nobility.

217
00:13:52,119 --> 00:13:53,400
Some of us are related to
influential households.

218
00:13:53,880 --> 00:13:55,200
We're classmates.

219
00:13:55,520 --> 00:13:56,400
She is not one of us.

220
00:13:57,119 --> 00:13:58,239
You might not be afraid.

221
00:13:58,479 --> 00:14:00,320
I'm afraid I get implicated.

222
00:14:01,119 --> 00:14:02,479
You're gossiping about me.

223
00:14:03,159 --> 00:14:04,599
Both of you sure are bold.

224
00:14:07,359 --> 00:14:09,559
If I hear this again in the academy,

225
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:11,320
regardless of who it is,

226
00:14:12,440 --> 00:14:13,599
both of you will be cast out.

227
00:14:17,640 --> 00:14:18,520
I have a question.

228
00:14:35,880 --> 00:14:36,559
How is she doing?

229
00:14:37,840 --> 00:14:39,119
Why wouldn't you check on her yourself?

230
00:14:40,520 --> 00:14:41,400
Xiaoman is sick.

231
00:14:41,760 --> 00:14:43,640
I came to apply a leave on her behalf.

232
00:14:44,679 --> 00:14:45,799
If there's nothing else,

233
00:14:46,119 --> 00:14:46,960
I shall take my leave.

234
00:14:47,300 --> 00:14:49,820
(There's no shortcut and no end
to studying)

235
00:14:53,159 --> 00:14:53,719
We utterly

236
00:14:53,719 --> 00:14:55,039
offended them.

237
00:14:56,719 --> 00:14:57,359
What are you going to do?

238
00:14:57,919 --> 00:14:58,960
How will you apologise?

239
00:14:59,280 --> 00:15:00,119
Why should I apologise?

240
00:15:00,880 --> 00:15:01,760
I did nothing wrong.

241
00:15:02,799 --> 00:15:03,479
Let's go to class.

242
00:15:04,320 --> 00:15:04,840
Hanchen.

243
00:15:06,799 --> 00:15:08,119
Let's put Xiaoman's matter aside.

244
00:15:08,479 --> 00:15:09,440
Another letter came from the capital.

245
00:15:10,280 --> 00:15:10,919
This time,

246
00:15:11,280 --> 00:15:12,840
it's a personal letter
with the prince's seal.

247
00:15:16,919 --> 00:15:18,719
Is he pestering me to
marry Shen Zhaowen?

248
00:15:21,239 --> 00:15:22,159
That depends if Shen family

249
00:15:22,159 --> 00:15:23,039
would agree to the marriage.

250
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:24,720
Things at Wujiang Prefecture

251
00:15:24,760 --> 00:15:26,159
are rather peaceful for now.

252
00:15:27,200 --> 00:15:28,320
If the Emperor passes away,

253
00:15:29,919 --> 00:15:30,719
(Family letter)
I'll be the first sacrifice

254
00:15:30,719 --> 00:15:32,000
for the new emperor.

255
00:15:35,400 --> 00:15:36,119
Wait, you...

256
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:39,280
Prepare a variety of textile
and tonics tonight.

257
00:15:39,880 --> 00:15:40,520
I need them.

258
00:15:41,919 --> 00:15:42,559
Well...

259
00:15:42,799 --> 00:15:44,080
Why did he tear the letter apart?

260
00:15:51,559 --> 00:15:52,039
Come here.

261
00:15:56,679 --> 00:15:57,359
Xiaoman.

262
00:15:58,440 --> 00:16:00,200
In my opinion, you should forget it.

263
00:16:01,000 --> 00:16:01,960
At this point,

264
00:16:01,960 --> 00:16:03,159
it's useless to think about it.

265
00:16:05,239 --> 00:16:05,880
Listen to me.

266
00:16:06,280 --> 00:16:08,840
Attend class with me tomorrow.

267
00:16:09,039 --> 00:16:09,960
Ignore them.

268
00:16:10,479 --> 00:16:11,440
Director Xu said,

269
00:16:11,719 --> 00:16:13,479
Teacher Liu's Poetry Competition
will be held in two days.

270
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:14,599
It will take the load off your mind.

271
00:16:16,479 --> 00:16:17,679
What is that?

272
00:16:18,280 --> 00:16:19,280
Lady, it's your turn.

273
00:16:21,200 --> 00:16:22,520
Don't you know who Teacher Liu is?

274
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:24,440
That's Liu Sanbian.

275
00:16:25,239 --> 00:16:26,919
Every year,
the performers of Wujiang Prefecture

276
00:16:27,880 --> 00:16:29,119
are obligated to participate
in Teacher Liu's competition.

