00:27:33,520 --> 00:27:34,280
Back then, Master Han

562
00:27:34,280 --> 00:27:36,000
taught me calligraphy as well.

563
00:27:36,359 --> 00:27:38,400
You said, although Hanchen is cheeky,

564
00:27:38,400 --> 00:27:40,760
his techniques exceed mine.

565
00:27:48,119 --> 00:27:49,280
Are you really going to help Congwen

566
00:27:49,280 --> 00:27:50,239
win the fan?

567
00:27:50,520 --> 00:27:51,839
Isn't it too difficult of a task?

568
00:27:56,680 --> 00:27:57,680
Are you trying to acquire
Teacher Liu's fan

569
00:27:57,680 --> 00:27:59,199
for Li Congwen?

570
00:28:02,319 --> 00:28:03,439
Do not poke your nose
into other's business.

571
00:28:03,439 --> 00:28:04,239
Have you heard of that?

572
00:28:04,479 --> 00:28:05,319
Do not tell anyone.

573
00:28:05,319 --> 00:28:06,119
Otherwise, I'd give you an earful.

574
00:28:06,560 --> 00:28:08,319
Fine, I can keep it a secret.

575
00:28:08,479 --> 00:28:09,560
However, you have to tell me

576
00:28:09,800 --> 00:28:11,439
why you're doing this for Li Congwen.

577
00:28:15,680 --> 00:28:16,719
The gazebo is chosen.

578
00:28:17,040 --> 00:28:17,760
Chunhui Pavilion.

579
00:28:17,959 --> 00:28:18,880
Let's head over there.

580
00:28:19,479 --> 00:28:20,239
It's for her to study.

581
00:28:20,239 --> 00:28:20,680
Let's go.

582
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:23,000
Boyang.

583
00:28:23,239 --> 00:28:23,880
Where's Hanchen?

584
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:25,439
Here he comes.

585
00:28:40,199 --> 00:28:41,479
These are the rules of
Flying Flower Game.

586
00:28:44,239 --> 00:28:44,560
Let me take a look.

587
00:28:44,560 --> 00:28:45,520
For this quarter's poetry competition,

588
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:46,760
(The rules of Flying Flower Game)
there are two sets of rules.

589
00:28:47,079 --> 00:28:47,959
The first is Flying Flower Game.

590
00:28:48,599 --> 00:28:49,400
The second is the ability
to compose poems.

591
00:28:50,479 --> 00:28:51,599
The theme for
the Flying Flower Game is

592
00:28:52,319 --> 00:28:52,880
"flowers".

593
00:28:53,599 --> 00:28:55,520
All of you shall answer in order.

594
00:28:56,040 --> 00:28:57,640
Write down the correct verses

595
00:28:57,760 --> 00:28:58,839
and present them.

596
00:29:00,319 --> 00:29:01,719
I'm not going to stay for long.

597
00:29:01,959 --> 00:29:03,400
Thus, I prepared a few
verses for all of you.

598
00:29:03,959 --> 00:29:05,160
You may memorise them

599
00:29:05,359 --> 00:29:06,199
and ponder upon them

600
00:29:06,640 --> 00:29:07,800
to be inspired.

601
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,400
Xingzhou.

602
00:29:15,800 --> 00:29:16,719
Xingzhou, where are you going?

603
00:29:19,439 --> 00:29:20,160
Ignore him.

604
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:20,880
He's always like that.

605
00:29:20,880 --> 00:29:21,680
He's eccentric.

606
00:29:25,920 --> 00:29:26,640
Xingzhou.

607
00:29:32,839 --> 00:29:34,520
How could you steal
Zhong Ziyan's moneybag?

608
00:29:34,959 --> 00:29:35,959
You're wrong.

609
00:29:36,239 --> 00:29:37,560
I did not steal.

610
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,079
I'm keeping it for him.

611
00:29:39,079 --> 00:29:40,000
I'll return it to him later.

612
00:29:47,839 --> 00:29:48,400
Assistant.

613
00:29:49,920 --> 00:29:50,479
Have some tea.

614
00:29:53,760 --> 00:29:54,319
Thank you.

615
00:30:06,479 --> 00:30:07,079
Fellow scholars.

616
00:30:07,560 --> 00:30:09,239
Let us begin.

617
00:30:19,599 --> 00:30:21,640
Sun Kaikai of Liulian Pavilion.

618
00:30:22,359 --> 00:30:24,239
Night has come,
the swallow has yet to return.

619
00:30:24,560 --> 00:30:27,079
The scenery cast with rain and
fog seemed wretched and delicate.

620
00:30:32,880 --> 00:30:33,439
Not bad.

621
00:30:33,959 --> 00:30:35,400
The great poet of Tang Dynasty,

622
00:30:36,040 --> 00:30:38,160
Dai Shulun's Shuxi Pavilion.

623
00:30:39,880 --> 00:30:40,560
Reward him the flower.

624
00:30:40,839 --> 00:30:41,719
Bravo!

625
00:30:42,000 --> 00:30:42,640
Bravo!

626
00:30:46,400 --> 00:30:48,520
(Shen Yan of Xiaoyue Pavilion.)

627
00:30:49,280 --> 00:30:51,199
(Despite the urge of the night breeze,)

628
00:30:51,719 --> 00:30:53,959
(the boat only floats by the shallows.)

629
00:31:17,640 --> 00:31:18,239
Hold on.

630
00:31:23,560 --> 00:31:24,239
Do not go.

631
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:25,599
Allow Boyang to present instead.

632
00:31:26,319 --> 00:31:26,920
Boyang.

633
00:31:27,839 --> 00:31:28,319
Hurry up.

634
00:31:29,880 --> 00:31:30,520
What?

635
00:31:32,119 --> 00:31:32,920
Why?

636
00:31:33,959 --> 00:31:35,199
You're clumsy.

637
00:31:35,319 --> 00:31:36,599
Do not ruin my brush and ink.

638
00:31:36,880 --> 00:31:37,800
Allow Boyang to go instead.

639
00:31:37,800 --> 00:31:38,520
Take a break.

640
00:31:40,280 --> 00:31:41,160
My father is still here.

641
00:31:41,160 --> 00:31:41,839
I can't go.

642
00:31:42,160 --> 00:31:43,119
You're my assistant.

643
00:31:43,119 --> 00:31:43,959
Why can't you go?

644
00:31:43,959 --> 00:31:45,040
You're so disobedient today.

645
00:31:45,439 --> 00:31:46,079
Assistant?

646
00:31:46,319 --> 00:31:47,319
Aren't we brothers?

647
00:31:47,319 --> 00:31:47,959
Yes, we are.

648
00:31:47,959 --> 00:31:49,079
That's why you need to help me out.

649
00:31:49,640 --> 00:31:50,319
Hurry up.

650
00:31:50,640 --> 00:31:51,359
Go on.

651
00:31:53,000 --> 00:31:53,880
Yan Boyang

652
00:31:54,319 --> 00:31:55,199
is moping around.

653
00:31:57,560 --> 00:31:58,439
Are you sure it'd work?

654
00:31:59,800 --> 00:32:00,680
Xingzhou is here.

655
00:32:00,680 --> 00:32:01,359
Don't worry.

656
00:32:10,040 --> 00:32:12,319
Zhao Xiaoqian of Chunhui Pavilion.

657
00:32:12,920 --> 00:32:14,680
In the tranquil mountains,
the osmanthus falls.

658
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:17,119
Loneliness echoes
through the placid night.

659
00:32:24,319 --> 00:32:26,400
This young man shows great technique.

660
00:32:27,199 --> 00:32:27,920
Award him with flower.

661
00:32:28,079 --> 00:32:29,560
Bravo!

662
00:32:30,280 --> 00:32:31,640
Bravo!

663
00:32:47,319 --> 00:32:47,839
Father.

664
00:32:48,920 --> 00:32:50,160
Hanchen invited me here today.

665
00:32:50,160 --> 00:32:51,199
He doesn't harbour ill intentions.

666
00:32:51,540 --> 00:32:53,820
(Magistrate of Wujiang, Yan Nengfu,
Yan Boyang's father)

667
00:32:54,079 --> 00:32:54,920
You were right.

668
00:32:57,199 --> 00:32:58,560
I said, what you did was right.

669
00:32:59,680 --> 00:33:00,439
Currently,

670
00:33:00,760 --> 00:33:02,959
the situation in
the imperial court is unstable.

671
00:33:03,599 --> 00:33:04,199
You

672
00:33:04,439 --> 00:33:05,880
are doing the right thing today.

673
00:33:06,160 --> 00:33:08,479
You should plan for yourself.

674
00:33:09,359 --> 00:33:10,920
Do not be swayed by
the opinions of others.

675
00:33:11,239 --> 00:33:13,319
Take hold of your own future.

676
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,400
Father,

677
00:33:14,400 --> 00:33:15,319
what are you talking about?

678
00:33:15,520 --> 00:33:17,199
Hanchen and I are brothers.

679
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:18,640
Look at you.

680
00:33:19,239 --> 00:33:20,520
Are you a fool?

681
00:33:21,560 --> 00:33:22,800
He's Commandery Prince of Julu.

682
00:33:23,319 --> 00:33:24,680
You expect to be his friend?

683
00:33:25,280 --> 00:33:27,079
You should know your position.

684
00:33:28,839 --> 00:33:29,479
No, father.

685
00:33:29,959 --> 00:33:30,239
This...

686
00:33:30,239 --> 00:33:31,000
That's enough.

687
00:33:31,199 --> 00:33:31,920
You should get back.

688
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:33,319
Go on.

689
00:33:39,520 --> 00:33:40,959
I heard of a young man
who came from the west.

690
00:33:41,400 --> 00:33:42,280
He claims to be

691
00:33:42,280 --> 00:33:43,040
the Head of Nencao Hall.

692
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,000
He writes poetry for others

693
00:33:44,199 --> 00:33:45,239
for a tael of silver.

694
00:33:45,719 --> 00:33:47,199
Many noble men and ladies

695
00:33:47,199 --> 00:33:48,119
consult him.

696
00:33:50,160 --> 00:33:51,640
Isn't this the second son of Yan family?

697
00:33:52,599 --> 00:33:53,839
Since when did he

698
00:33:54,319 --> 00:33:55,640
become a male attendant just like us?

699
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:57,479
You have no idea.

700
00:33:57,760 --> 00:33:58,680
The second son of Yan family

701
00:33:58,680 --> 00:34:00,280
has always been
the assistant of the Commandery Prince.

702
00:34:00,599 --> 00:34:01,959
He pleased the Commandery Prince.

703
00:34:02,319 --> 00:34:03,520
He has a great future ahead of him.

704
00:34:03,760 --> 00:34:04,640
He's different

705
00:34:04,719 --> 00:34:05,640
from the rest of us.

706
00:34:05,880 --> 00:34:06,800
What are you talking about?

707
00:34:07,239 --> 00:34:08,439
Mind your words.

708
00:34:16,679 --> 00:34:17,399
Assistant.

709
00:34:19,639 --> 00:34:20,239
Come here.

710
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:26,520
Have some tea.

711
00:34:28,040 --> 00:34:28,959
I don't want any.

712
00:34:29,719 --> 00:34:31,760
Commandery Prince shouldn't
pour tea for the attendant.

713
00:34:32,600 --> 00:34:33,520
What are you afraid of?

714
00:34:33,679 --> 00:34:34,840
I even fed Zhao Mao...

715
00:34:35,520 --> 00:34:36,320
What did you feed him?

716
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:41,959
It's none of your business.

717
00:34:50,239 --> 00:34:51,239
I'm leaving these here.

718
00:34:51,520 --> 00:34:52,159
I'm leaving.

719
00:34:56,479 --> 00:34:57,520
What's wrong with Boyang?

720
00:34:59,159 --> 00:34:59,879
I'll check out on him.

721
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:02,600
Zhanzhi.

722
00:35:04,199 --> 00:35:04,479
Zhanzhi.

723
00:35:04,479 --> 00:35:05,399
What's wrong with him?

724
00:35:05,760 --> 00:35:06,399
Zhanzhi.

725
00:35:07,600 --> 00:35:08,439
What's going on?

726
00:35:10,280 --> 00:35:11,439
Is something wrong?

727
00:35:11,520 --> 00:35:12,479
We came here together.

728
00:35:12,479 --> 00:35:13,840
The last round isn't over yet.

729
00:35:14,159 --> 00:35:15,479
Why did you leave on your own?

730
00:35:17,800 --> 00:35:18,520
Am I going to stay here

731
00:35:18,760 --> 00:35:20,479
and be ordered around
as an assistant?

732
00:35:21,520 --> 00:35:22,479
What are you talking about?

733
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:23,800
What else can I say?

734
00:35:24,120 --> 00:35:25,760
I came to my senses today.

735
00:35:25,760 --> 00:35:26,919
I've finally learned the reality.

736
00:35:27,840 --> 00:35:28,719
I'm telling you.

737
00:35:29,159 --> 00:35:30,000
Your Highness,

738
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,879
may you enjoy the view.

739
00:35:33,239 --> 00:35:34,280
What's going on with you?

740
00:35:36,040 --> 00:35:37,199
I had no idea

741
00:35:37,840 --> 00:35:40,360
Your Highness were concerned
about Teacher Liu's Poetry Competition.

742
00:35:40,520 --> 00:35:41,639
Xiaoman wants the fan.

743
00:35:41,639 --> 00:35:43,080
Everyone is helping her out.

744
00:35:44,639 --> 00:35:46,000
Xiaoman wants the fan?

745
00:35:46,239 --> 00:35:47,080
Are you a fool?

746
00:35:48,040 --> 00:35:50,000
Xiaoman isn't going to
give the fan to you.

747
00:35:50,280 --> 00:35:51,439
The fan is for Li Su!

748
00:36:00,199 --> 00:36:00,840
What's the matter?

749
00:36:01,679 --> 00:36:02,520
Are you going to hit me?

750
00:36:05,000 --> 00:36:05,679
Go ahead and hit me here.

751
00:36:06,199 --> 00:36:07,399
You're the Commandery Prince after all.

752
00:36:07,560 --> 00:36:08,840
I can take it. Go ahead and hit me.

753
00:36:09,360 --> 00:36:09,959
Come on.

754
00:36:15,639 --> 00:36:16,199
Why wouldn't you hit me?

755
00:36:26,679 --> 00:36:27,679
What's wrong with Yan Boyang?

756
00:36:27,800 --> 00:36:29,159
Why do you need Teacher Liu's fan?

757
00:36:31,120 --> 00:36:31,600
I...

758
00:36:32,879 --> 00:36:34,199
Do you take me as a fool?

759
00:36:36,360 --> 00:36:37,760
By making me participate
in the competition,

760
00:36:38,199 --> 00:36:39,199
winning the fan,

761
00:36:39,560 --> 00:36:40,679
and gifting it to Li Su instead.

762
00:36:42,000 --> 00:36:43,199
Does it please you?

763
00:36:44,399 --> 00:36:44,959
No.

764
00:36:46,159 --> 00:36:46,919
Xie Xiaoman,

765
00:36:48,320 --> 00:36:49,199
good for you.

766
00:36:50,399 --> 00:36:51,520
I'm Commandery Prince of Julu,

767
00:36:51,520 --> 00:36:53,040
yet I was completely fooled by you.

768
00:36:54,600 --> 00:36:55,199
Well done.

769
00:36:58,479 --> 00:36:59,159
Zhao Xiaoqian.

770
00:36:59,679 --> 00:37:00,520
Let me explain.

771
00:37:01,120 --> 00:37:01,800
Do not touch me.

772
00:37:06,919 --> 00:37:07,479
Xiaoman,

773
00:37:07,479 --> 00:37:08,199
where are you going?

774
00:37:08,479 --> 00:37:09,479
He brought me here.

775
00:37:09,679 --> 00:37:11,199
I need to explain the situation.

776
00:37:11,959 --> 00:37:12,800
At this point,

777
00:37:12,800 --> 00:37:14,199
it's a waste if you're leaving.

778
00:37:16,560 --> 00:37:17,199
How about this?

779
00:37:17,679 --> 00:37:18,520
I'll look for him on your behalf

780
00:37:18,679 --> 00:37:19,800
and clear the air.

781
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:21,679
Don't worry.

782
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:24,159
I'm off.

783
00:37:28,360 --> 00:37:29,040
Master.

784
00:37:29,520 --> 00:37:30,560
How are the things going?

785
00:37:30,800 --> 00:37:32,560
The boat is ready.

786
00:37:32,679 --> 00:37:34,360
Once he enters the boat,
he will not be able to leave.

787
00:37:34,919 --> 00:37:35,479
Good job.

788
00:37:36,199 --> 00:37:36,800
You're dismissed.

789
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:37,840
All right.

790
00:37:49,399 --> 00:37:50,199
Xie Xiaoman?

791
00:37:50,959 --> 00:37:51,679
What are you doing here?

792
00:37:52,639 --> 00:37:53,679
I came to tell you

793
00:37:54,000 --> 00:37:54,840
that Yan Boyang

794
00:37:54,840 --> 00:37:56,120
is trapped in the boat.

795
00:37:56,479 --> 00:37:57,120
Master

796
00:37:57,120 --> 00:37:58,679
wants me to inform His Highness

797
00:37:58,919 --> 00:38:00,520
so he may head to his rescue.

798
00:38:00,800 --> 00:38:01,399
If

799
00:38:01,479 --> 00:38:03,199
Yan Boyang is trapped for long,

800
00:38:03,479 --> 00:38:04,879
what should we do if
something goes wrong?

801
00:38:05,360 --> 00:38:06,600
That's why you should
inform him quickly.

802
00:38:10,320 --> 00:38:11,120
Zhao Xiaoqian.

803
00:38:25,879 --> 00:38:26,560
Attendant.

804
00:38:27,399 --> 00:38:28,199
Excuse me,

805
00:38:28,399 --> 00:38:30,040
have you seen Yan Boyang?

806
00:38:30,600 --> 00:38:31,199
I'm not sure.

807
00:38:34,199 --> 00:38:35,360
Look, that's him.

808
00:38:36,320 --> 00:38:37,120
Based on the appearance,

809
00:38:37,120 --> 00:38:38,639
it doesn't resemble
a son of a noble household.

810
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:40,000
It resembles a woman.

811
00:38:40,000 --> 00:38:40,600
Whatever.

812
00:38:40,840 --> 00:38:41,679
We took the money for this.

813
00:38:41,959 --> 00:38:42,600
Let's go.

814
00:38:47,479 --> 00:38:48,520
Handsome man.

815
00:38:48,520 --> 00:38:49,639
Let's drink to our heart's content.

816
00:38:49,639 --> 00:38:50,560
Let's go, handsome.

817
00:38:50,560 --> 00:38:50,879
Let's go.

818
00:38:50,879 --> 00:38:51,399
Let go of me.

819
00:38:51,399 --> 00:38:51,840
Have a cup.

820
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,639
No, I'm not going.

821
00:38:52,639 --> 00:38:53,520
Let's go.

822
00:39:01,439 --> 00:39:02,040
How did it go?

823
00:39:04,399 --> 00:39:05,639
I couldn't find the Commandery Prince,

824
00:39:05,639 --> 00:39:07,320
but I met his female attendant.

825
00:39:08,080 --> 00:39:09,439
I ordered her to
inform Zhao Xiaoqian.

826
00:39:09,800 --> 00:39:10,679
With my identity,

827
00:39:10,679 --> 00:39:12,320
he'd grow suspicious.

828
00:39:13,399 --> 00:39:14,520
However, do not worry.

829
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:15,320
Once Zhao Xiaoqian

830
00:39:15,320 --> 00:39:16,800
enters the boat,

831
00:39:17,040 --> 00:39:18,080
even if nothing happens,

832
00:39:18,080 --> 00:39:19,679
we can spread rumours about it.

833
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:20,679
If this incident was made known,

834
00:39:20,679 --> 00:39:21,959
his reputation will be tarnished.

835
00:39:22,520 --> 00:39:23,080
Great.

836
00:39:25,040 --> 00:39:25,520
Master,

837
00:39:26,120 --> 00:39:27,199
isn't that Mr. Yan?

838
00:39:27,360 --> 00:39:28,399
I don't know what's wrong with him.

839
00:39:28,600 --> 00:39:29,840
He played three rounds
of chess here

840
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,639
and wouldn't leave.

841
00:39:32,800 --> 00:39:34,199
He walked directly into the trap.

842
00:39:35,479 --> 00:39:36,479
I shall play a few rounds with him.

843
00:39:39,199 --> 00:39:39,959
Mr. Yan.

844
00:39:41,080 --> 00:39:41,679
Get out of my way.

